  <sect2 role="package">
    <title/>

    <para>The XML::Parser module is a Perl interface to James Clark's
    XML parser, Expat.</para>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
      <segtitle>&diskspace;</segtitle>

